findings.title: Out of gas
findings.description: The function manageBots() uses a loop to add/remove bot addresses and will be aborted with OUT_OF_GAS exception if there is a long addresses list.

findings.title: Sending tokens to dead address instead of really burning (decreasing total supply)
findings.description: Tokens are sent to a dead address rather than being burned, which does not decrease the total supply.

findings.title: DoS with block gas limit
findings.description: The contract may be vulnerable to Denial of Service (DoS) attacks due to the block gas limit.
